<template>
  <main-header>Список постов</main-header>
  <posts-list :posts="POSTS"/>
</template>

<script>
import PostsList from '@/components/posts/PostsList.vue'
import { mapActions, mapGetters } from 'vuex';
export default {
 components: {
   PostsList,
 },

 data:() => ({

 }),

 methods: {
   ...mapActions([
     'GET_POSTS_FROM_API',
   ]),
 },

 computed: {
   ...mapGetters([
     'POSTS',
   ]),
 },

 mounted() {
   this.GET_POSTS_FROM_API()
 }
}
</script>

</style>
